<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="light-v">light <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /laɪt/    美 /laɪt/  </p>
<p>(lit / lighted, lit / lighted) vt &amp; vi</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>点燃：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When he comes, we'll light the candles and sing "Happy Birthday" together for him.
当他进来时，我们会点燃蜡烛并且一起为他唱“生日快乐”歌。</p><footer>2012 全国书面表达</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The match won't light.
这火柴划不着。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>照亮：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The painting shows a beautiful house lit by lights from inside , surrounded by the darkness of night.
这副画描绘的是一座室内被灯光照亮、室外被夜色笼罩的美丽的房子。</p><footer>北师大新必修③ – 7改</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="light-up">light up</h3>
<p>1.<strong>照亮；喜形于色：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>New Year's fireworks lit up the sky over the city.
新年焰火照亮了整个城市的天空。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Her face lit up with pleasure. 
她的脸上露出欣喜的神色。</p></div>

<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>lighten /'laɪtn/ v   </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>lighten the load
减轻负担</p></div>

<p>lighter /'laɪtə(r)/ n [C]   </p></div>